name: Elijah Marshall

His main interests include hiking, coding, and reading, upholding values such as honesty, ambition, and family. Although he doesn't have pets or children right now, he is open to having kids in the future. He drinks occasionally, doesn't smoke, use marijuana, or other drugs, and leans liberal in politics while being agnostic. As a Pisces, and someone who is active and enjoys taking care of his physical health, he is seeking monogamy and a long-term relationship. He identifies as an ISTJ personality type.
